      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 20:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朱利安尼的儿子、前助手在资产搜查中收到传票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/giuliani-s-son-former-aide-hit-with-subpoenas-in-asset-search</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲁道夫·朱利安尼的债权人扩大了对这位前纽约市长财务状况的调查，周五在他的破产案中发出了十几张传票。]]></description>
